---
title: Chermoula Aubergine & Mushroom Stew with Couscous, Feta and Courgette Salad
description: We love good Aubergine and Mushroom Stew and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chermoula-aubgerine-mushroom-stew-3d720e99-9b17895c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/chermoula-aubgerine-mushroom-stew-5d4a8211af67d600090423d3-c8b9b317.pdf
author: Mimi Morley
cuisine: Moroccan
nutrition:
  calories: 563 kcal
  fat: 14 g
  saturated fat: 9 g
  carbohydrates: 80 g
  sugar: 22 g
